{"tid":1719815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"67暴動 工聯會造成嚴重傷亡","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T07:36:47.000Z","uid":97662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2022f4369f373c4c287c820a9c9ba33fa839fe","tid":1719815,"uid":97662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"//「六七暴動」又稱「1967 年香港左派暴亂／Hong Kong 1967 Leftist Riots」，香港親中共左派（如工聯會）受中國文化大革命影響，加上港英政府腐敗貪污，底層民眾生活困難，左派執著「反英抗暴」的理念，展開對抗政府的暴動，由最初的罷工、示威，發展至後來的暗殺、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">炸彈放置</span></span>和槍戰。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴動期間，最少造成包括 11 名警務人員殉職在內的 52 人死亡，包括 212 名警員在內的802人受傷，1,936 人被檢控；事件中總共涉及 1,167 個炸彈。</span></strong></span>//<br />\n<br />\n痴孖根垃圾工聯會炸彈都出埋，好恐怖<br />\n<br />\nsorry for old news<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://photoblog.hk/255367/%25E5%25BE%259E%25E7%258F%258D%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E8%2588%258A%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2598%25AF/&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjbxcmYlunlAhXE7GEKHY0rA3wQFjAMegQIBBAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw0DpPh2wyFjeAtht_VazP8j&amp;cshid=1573716619947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F255367%2F%2525E5%2525BE%25259E%2525E7%25258F%25258D%2525E8%2525B2%2525B4%2525E8%252588%25258A%2525E7%252585%2525A7%2525E7%252589%252587%2525E4%2525BA%252586%2525E8%2525A7%2525A3%2525EF%2525BC%25258C%2525E5%2525B7%2525A5%2525E8%252581%2525AF%2525E6%25259C%252583%2525E6%25258E%2525A8%2525E5%25258B%252595%2525E7%25259A%252584%2525E3%252580%25258C%2525E5%252585%2525AD%2525E4%2525B8%252583%2525E6%25259A%2525B4%2525E5%25258B%252595%2525